      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Clean title opportunity for someone seeking an inexpensive project or basic transportation. This car is in poor condition and shows significant wear, age, and likely needs repairs and attention before it can be considered dependable for daily use. That said, it could still make sense for a handy buyer, first project, or budget-minded shopper who understands what it is and is looking for value at the right price.",
