    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical choice for a handy buyer, first-time driver, or anyone seeking inexpensive transportation with room to improve. It offers solid value as an affordable project or everyday runabout, with straightforward appeal for someone who understands how to make the most of a lower-cost vehicle. Priced to move and represented honestly, this is a chance to secure dependable utility at an accessible entry point.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right owner? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great opportunity for someone who wants a budget-friendly daily, a learner car, or a tidy little project. It\u2019s being sold as-is and priced to reflect its age and wear, but it still has plenty to offer for someone practical who knows a good value when they see one. If you want honest motoring without spending a fortune, this could be the one.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project with a strong-running powertrain foundation and good enthusiast upside. The engine pulls cleanly, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis still feels composed enough to make this a worthwhile fixer, parts donor, or budget driver build. Cosmetic wear and age-related needs are present, but the core mechanical package feels honest and serviceable. If you want an affordable entry point with usable hardware and room to improve, this one has the right bones.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
